info.name: Chicken Tom Yum Soup
info.description: Indulge in our Thai Chicken Soup, a flawless harmony of hot and sour flavors. Bursting with Thai herbs, fragrant lemongrass, lemon leaves, and tender chicken, this soup achieves the perfect balance, delivering a delightful symphony of tastes in every spoonful. Immerse yourself in the richness of Thai culinary artistry. No Added MSG.

info.name: Paneer In Sweet Chilli Sauce
info.description: Savor the exquisite taste of deep-fried paneer, expertly tossed in a sweet and spicy chili sauce. Each bite bursts with flavorful goodness, creating a delightful harmony of textures and tastes. No Added MSG.

info.name: Chicken Wings In Sweet Chilli Sauce
info.description: Delight in our fried chicken wings, perfectly tossed in a sweet and spicy sauce that boasts a dominant blend of sweetness and chili flavor. A mouthwatering experience in every bite. No Added MSG.

info.name: Schezwan Egg
info.description: Savor the crunch of our Crispy Fried Boiled Egg, perfectly tossed in our house-special Schezwan mayo. An irresistible combination of textures and flavors awaits in every bite. No Added MSG.

info.name: Crispy Hot Garlic Chicken
info.description: Indulge in our tender, crispy chicken bites, where bold garlic flavors meet a subtle hint of heat. A delightful culinary experience that promises a symphony of taste and texture in every bite. No Added MSG.

info.name: Indo Chilli Fish
info.description: Experience the perfect fusion of flavors with our Fried Fish, bell peppers, and onions, expertly tossed in our special Indo-Chilli sauce. A delectable harmony that tantalizes your taste buds. No Added MSG.

info.name: Veg Triple Schezwan Fried Rice Regular
info.description: Indulge in our Triple Schezwan Fried Rice, a beloved Indo-Chinese fusion delight. This dish merges the bold flavors of Schezwan and fried rice, featuring a medley of vegetables and Schezwan sauce stir-fried with precooked noodles and rice. Served with a tantalizing soy sauce-based Manchurian gravy, accompanied by three Veg Coins and crowned with crispy fried noodles. A flavor-packed culinary experience in every bite. No Added MSG.

info.name: Chicken Triple Schezwan Fried Rice Regular
info.description: Savor our Triple Schezwan Fried Rice, a delectable Indo-Chinese fusion featuring the perfect blend of Schezwan and fried rice. Stir-fried with precooked noodles, rice, vegetables, and sauted chicken in Schezwan sauce, this dish is served with a soy sauce-based Manchurian gravy. Delight in the addition of three pieces of fried chicken and a crispy noodle topping, creating a flavorful culinary experience. No Added MSG.
